## Download the new reference genome and get it ready to be used.
## Note, this new reference genome replaces the previous one and all samples need to be re-mapped to it.

wget ...

## Now, we are using sinteractive, to unzip the reference genome, index it for samtools as well as for bwa.
sinteractive
## 1) Unzip
gunzip Frufa_PR_May2026.fa.gz   # produces genome.fa

## 2) FASTA index for samtools, bcftools, etc.
module load biokit
samtools faidx Frufa_PR_May2026.fa    # creates genome.fa.fai

## 3) Index for your aligner (pick one):
## for BWA
bwa index Frufa_PR_May2026.fa         # creates .amb, .ann, .bwt, .pac, .sa
